2054.subject: HPWE
2054.descrlong: The Foundation of Channeling Energy and Self-Empowerment. Students learn short, powerful, basic practices that can be done daily to increase and balance their life force energy. Explains theory and guides students through the practices, sharing a "map" of how to induce inner Chi flow. In this way, students learn to tap into their own energy in order to heal and detoxify their organs, and to reduce emotional and physical stress. (Offered every semester.)
